name: Billie Boullet
description:
Here's a textual inversion of the british actress Billie Boullet, who plays in the excellent serie "A Small Light" (as Anne Frank). Before someone ask me, yes she's 18 !

This model seems to be pretty good as is, but I'm planning to fine tune it a bit.

It is very accurate on closeup and medium range shot but you might want to use the inpaint function for long shot.

Enjoy ! :)
